# Quick GreenSock tutorial
Egghead.io beginner tutorial for 'Creating Amazing Animations with GreeSock'

##Setup GreenSock as a Module with Parcel
First create a new project forlder, open a terminal in it and install parcel (npm or yarn)
`> npm install parcel-bundler`

Then create the package.json file and copy this code line inside (assuming index.html is your entry point):

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "parcel index.html"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "parcel-bundler": "^1.12.4"
  }
}
```
Run the application : `npm run dev`

See. 
- Parcel documentation : [Parcel](https://parceljs.org/getting_started.html)
- Egghead tutorial : [Egghead](https://egghead.io/lessons/greensock-setup-greensock-as-a-module-with-parcel)
